# To Do List

A simple To Do List application built with HTML, Tailwind CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- Add tasks to the list.
- Mark tasks as completed by clicking on them (the task will be crossed out).
- Delete tasks by double-clicking on them.
- Task appearance animation when added.

## Project Structure

### Front-End

The front-end is built using:

- **HTML**: Provides the structure of the page.
- **Tailwind CSS**: Used for styling the page, leveraging utility classes for layout and design.
- **Custom CSS**: For custom animations.

### Back-End

The back-end uses plain JavaScript to handle the following interactions:

- Adding a task to the list.
- Marking a task as completed.
- Deleting a task from the list.

## Dependencies

- **Tailwind CSS**: Included via a CDN to style the user interface.
  
  ```html
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
